member.example:
    The following example demonstrates how to use the
    OnClientPaneCollapsed property. 




            <script type="text/javascript">

             function OnClientPaneCollapsedHandler(sender, eventArgs)

             {

             alert(eventArgs.paneObj.ID);

             }

            </script>



            <radspl:RadPane ID="RadPane1"

             runat= "server"

			OnClientPaneCollapsed="OnClientPaneCollapsedHandler">

            ....

            </radspl:RadPane>

The following example demonstrates how to use the OnClientBeforePaneCollapse property.
<script type="text/javascript">
function OnClientBeforePaneCollapseHandler(sender, eventArgs)
{
alert(eventArgs.paneObj.ID);
return true;//false to cancel the event
}
</script>
<radspl:RadPane ID="RadPane1"
runat= "server"
OnClientBeforePaneCollapse="OnClientBeforePaneCollapseHandler">
....
</radspl:RadPane>

